ABRT docker container
=====================

This image expects that the host have 'abrt-atomic' package installed and
'abrt-coredum-helper' service is running.

To run ABRT container issue the following command:

$ docker run -d --privileged -v /var/tmp:/var/tmp -v /var/run:/var/run -v /var/log:/var/log -v /var/lib/abrt:/var/lib/abrt -v /:/host --pid=host --net=host --name NAME IMAGE
